# Brownfield Development Workflow

## Overview
This project follows the BMad (Brownfield Modernization and Development) framework for iterative improvement of existing systems.

## Phases
1. **Phase 1**: Core MVP (Receipt Capture, Management, Export)
2. **Phase 2**: Authentication & User Management
3. **Phase 3**: Advanced Features (Analytics, Integrations)

## Development Process
1. Story Planning
2. Technical Design
3. Implementation
4. Testing
5. Review
6. Deployment

## Git Workflow
- Feature branches from main
- PR reviews required
- CI/CD automated testing
- Staged rollouts
